## 9. Integration with other GDDs

| Concern | Defined in |
|---------|-----------|
| Map generation (zones, nodes, edges, function-node placement) | `MapGDD.md` |
| Foe types, stats, day-based scaling, sight/aggro, evolution, loot hooks | `FOES.gdd` |
| Wonder items, cores, trader economy, equipment slots | **Wonder Item GDD** (separate doc) |
| Plantation mechanics (slot counts, seed types, growth, harvest) | **Plantation GDD** (separate doc) |
| Boss design (phases, arenas, unique skills) | `FOES.gdd` §8 (TBD) |
| Question-mark event content | This doc §6 (TODO) |
| Level 5 & 6 content / run-performance gating | This doc §8 (TODO) |
| Meta-progression (persistent unlocks between runs) | TBD — future GDD |

